Text.SourceString: Patrol's been calm today, thank the tides. It's always good when the sea's as peaceful as a sleeping whale.
Text.LocalizedString: Patrol's been calm today, thank the tides. It's always good when the sea's as peaceful as a sleeping whale.

Text.SourceString: Had to chase off some nosy barracudas near the gate. They're more bark than bite, but can't let 'em near the kingdom.
Text.LocalizedString: Had to chase off some nosy barracudas near the gate. They're more bark than bite, but can't let 'em near the kingdom.

Text.SourceString: The day shift's as quiet as a starfish today. Gives me time to think, watch over the kingdom.
Text.LocalizedString: The day shift's as quiet as a starfish today. Gives me time to think, watch over the kingdom.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Etna</>'s planning a seaweed feast tonight.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Etna</>'s planning a seaweed feast tonight.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Denali</> caught a sneaky eel trying to slip past the gate. No one's pulling the seaweed over her eyes, that's for sure.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Denali</> caught a sneaky eel trying to slip past the gate. No one's pulling the seaweed over her eyes, that's for sure.

Text.SourceString: I tell ya, watching <NPCName>Denali</> at the gate, it's like seeing a young me, only sharper and more patient.
Text.LocalizedString: I tell ya, watching <NPCName>Denali</> at the gate, it's like seeing a young me, only sharper and more patient.

Text.SourceString: Last night, we had a family swim. We went up to the shore and enjoyed the view.
Text.LocalizedString: Last night, we had a family swim. We went up to the shore and enjoyed the view.

Text.SourceString: Next week, we're planning another family swim. <NPCName>Etna</>, <NPCName>Denali</>, and I will be drifting with the current, just like when <NPCName>Denali</> was just a little minnow.//<portrait=normal>Thinking of taking them up north this time, show them a different view.
Text.LocalizedString: Next week, we're planning another family swim. <NPCName>Etna</>, <NPCName>Denali</>, and I will be drifting with the current, just like when <NPCName>Denali</> was just a little minnow.//<portrait=normal>Thinking of taking them up north this time, show them a different view.

Text.SourceString: Thinkin' of grillin' some kelp tonight. Throw in a bit of plankton spice – <NPCName>Etna</> says it's my best dish.
Text.LocalizedString: Thinkin' of grillin' some kelp tonight. Throw in a bit of plankton spice – <NPCName>Etna</> says it's my best dish.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Etna</>'s making her famous coral crunchies. I tell ya, those things are addictive.//<portrait=happy>I'm bracing myself for some extra scales.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Etna</>'s making her famous coral crunchies. I tell ya, those things are addictive.//<portrait=happy>I'm bracing myself for some extra scales.

Text.SourceString: Caught a plump sea bass today. <NPCName>Etna</> made her best marinade. Oh, I'm looking forward to a grand feast!
Text.LocalizedString: Caught a plump sea bass today. <NPCName>Etna</> made her best marinade. Oh, I'm looking forward to a grand feast!

Text.SourceString: When I'm not on duty, I love tinkering with old trinkets. Found a human watch once, strange little thing.
Text.LocalizedString: When I'm not on duty, I love tinkering with old trinkets. Found a human watch once, strange little thing.

Text.SourceString: I've been teaching <NPCName>Denali</> how to carve stones. It's delicate work, like shaping the tides themselves.
Text.LocalizedString: I've been teaching <NPCName>Denali</> how to carve stones. It's delicate work, like shaping the tides themselves.

Text.SourceString: On quiet nights, I sometimes just float and gaze at the surface. The moonlight dancing on the water, it's mesmerizing.
Text.LocalizedString: On quiet nights, I sometimes just float and gaze at the surface. The moonlight dancing on the water, it's mesmerizing.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Etna</> and I, we sometimes race each other around the reef. She wins most times, but don't tell her I said that.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Etna</> and I, we sometimes race each other around the reef. She wins most times, but don't tell her I said that.

Text.SourceString: There's always something happening in the kingdom. I'm learning a lot, but sometimes I miss the tranquility of my old home, Atlantoria.
Text.LocalizedString: There's always something happening in the kingdom. I'm learning a lot, but sometimes I miss the tranquility of my old home, Atlantoria.

Text.SourceString: Lots of salmon here, huh? Not really my favorite, but it'll do.
Text.LocalizedString: Lots of salmon here, huh? Not really my favorite, but it'll do.

Text.SourceString: Kingdom food's different. Never ate so much labu before, but it's alright.
Text.LocalizedString: Kingdom food's different. Never ate so much labu before, but it's alright.

Text.SourceString: Guards here love to party. Loud for my taste, but it's kinda fun.
Text.LocalizedString: Guards here love to party. Loud for my taste, but it's kinda fun.

Text.SourceString: I miss the open spaces back home. The kingdom feels a bit cramped sometimes.
Text.LocalizedString: I miss the open spaces back home. The kingdom feels a bit cramped sometimes.

Text.SourceString: The tides are calm today. Perfect for a leisurely patrol around the kingdom's borders.
Text.LocalizedString: The tides are calm today. Perfect for a leisurely patrol around the kingdom's borders.

Text.SourceString: Caught a glimpse of a rare fish near the coral beds this morning. Reminds me why I love this place.
Text.LocalizedString: Caught a glimpse of a rare fish near the coral beds this morning. Reminds me why I love this place.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Denali</>'s been training hard lately. That kid's got the heart of a shark, strong and fearless.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Denali</>'s been training hard lately. That kid's got the heart of a shark, strong and fearless.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Etna</>'s planning to try a new recipe with sea berries tonight. Can't wait to taste what she comes up with.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Etna</>'s planning to try a new recipe with sea berries tonight. Can't wait to taste what she comes up with.

Text.SourceString: Just finished fixing up a leak in the barracks. It's not all about guarding; sometimes you've got to maintain the fort too.
Text.LocalizedString: Just finished fixing up a leak in the barracks. It's not all about guarding; sometimes you've got to maintain the fort too.

Text.SourceString: I've been mapping out some unexplored caverns around the kingdom. Never know what secrets they might hold.
Text.LocalizedString: I've been mapping out some unexplored caverns around the kingdom. Never know what secrets they might hold.

Text.SourceString: Had a meeting with the council about enhancing our defense strategies. Always planning, always preparing.
Text.LocalizedString: Had a meeting with the council about enhancing our defense strategies. Always planning, always preparing.

Text.SourceString: The garden's bounty is thanks to <NPCName>Etna</>'s green fins. She always makes sure there's plenty for the soldiers at the barracks.
Text.LocalizedString: The garden's bounty is thanks to <NPCName>Etna</>'s green fins. She always makes sure there's plenty for the soldiers at the barracks.

Text.SourceString: You should see the spread <NPCName>Etna</> sends to the barracks. It's like a feast – makes the whole team feel appreciated.
Text.LocalizedString: You should see the spread <NPCName>Etna</> sends to the barracks. It's like a feast – makes the whole team feel appreciated.

Text.SourceString: I'm a bit worried about the increasing killer shrimps sightings near the reef. Need to ensure everyone's safety.
Text.LocalizedString: I'm a bit worried about the increasing killer shrimps sightings near the reef. Need to ensure everyone's safety.

Text.SourceString: Lately, the tides have been unpredictable. It's concerning; we have to adjust our patrols accordingly.
Text.LocalizedString: Lately, the tides have been unpredictable. It's concerning; we have to adjust our patrols accordingly.

Text.SourceString: There's been talk of a strange shadow in the waters at night. I'll have to investigate; can't take any chances.
Text.LocalizedString: There's been talk of a strange shadow in the waters at night. I'll have to investigate; can't take any chances.

Text.SourceString: There's no place like the Sleepy Eel to unwind after a long shift. It's where we guards go to relax and share stories.
Text.LocalizedString: There's no place like the Sleepy Eel to unwind after a long shift. It's where we guards go to relax and share stories.

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Etna</> and I like to drop by for a quiet drink now and then.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Etna</> and I like to drop by for a quiet drink now and then.

Text.SourceString: The Sleepy Eel has the best sea brew in the kingdom. Their coral reef fizz is the best.
Text.LocalizedString: The Sleepy Eel has the best sea brew in the kingdom. Their coral reef fizz is the best.

Text.SourceString: Got a bit of a headache today. Must be from staring at the shimmering water for too long on patrol.
Text.LocalizedString: Got a bit of a headache today. Must be from staring at the shimmering water for too long on patrol.

Text.SourceString: Feeling a bit sluggish today. Maybe I swam too much yesterday.
Text.LocalizedString: Feeling a bit sluggish today. Maybe I swam too much yesterday.

Text.SourceString: Woke up with a stiff fin. Maybe I slept weird. A good swim should loosen it up.
Text.LocalizedString: Woke up with a stiff fin. Maybe I slept weird. A good swim should loosen it up.

Text.SourceString: The water's a bit chillier than usual this morning. Feels refreshing, actually.
Text.LocalizedString: The water's a bit chillier than usual this morning. Feels refreshing, actually.

Text.SourceString: Noticed some new fish around the reef today. The kingdom's waters are always full of surprises.
Text.LocalizedString: Noticed some new fish around the reef today. The kingdom's waters are always full of surprises.

Text.SourceString: Feeling energized today. There's something about the water's flow that just invigorates you.
Text.LocalizedString: Feeling energized today. There's something about the water's flow that just invigorates you.

Text.SourceString: You notice how <NPCName>Semeru</> never really lets his guard down, even off duty? Strange for one so young.//Can't help but wonder what he's been through.
Text.LocalizedString: You notice how <NPCName>Semeru</> never really lets his guard down, even off duty? Strange for one so young.//Can't help but wonder what he's been through.

Text.SourceString: He isn't one for small talk or smiles, more like an old sea turtle than a shark.//<portrait=happy>Okay, now I'm generalizing.
Text.LocalizedString: He isn't one for small talk or smiles, more like an old sea turtle than a shark.//<portrait=happy>Okay, now I'm generalizing.

Text.SourceString: I noticed you've been chatting with <NPCName>Semeru</> recently. Got an eye on him? Just so you know, he's single.//But be warned, he can be a tough nut to crack.
Text.LocalizedString: I noticed you've been chatting with <NPCName>Semeru</> recently. Got an eye on him? Just so you know, he's single.//But be warned, he can be a tough nut to crack.

Text.SourceString: Heh, I'd rather you marry him than my daughter. Not that she's interested...//<portrait=happy>He doesn't exactly strike me as the life of a holiday gathering.
Text.LocalizedString: Heh, I'd rather you marry him than my daughter. Not that she's interested...//<portrait=happy>He doesn't exactly strike me as the life of a holiday gathering.

Text.SourceString: Hello there, you must be my daughter's new friend. <NPCName>Denali</> has mentioned you.//<portrait=normal>I'm Tahat, her father. She's had nothing but good things to say about you.
Text.LocalizedString: Hello there, you must be my daughter's new friend. <NPCName>Denali</> has mentioned you.//<portrait=normal>I'm Tahat, her father. She's had nothing but good things to say about you.

Text.SourceString: It's great to finally meet you.
Text.LocalizedString: It's great to finally meet you.
